<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Britannia </h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The southwest quadrant of Calgary houses the small but upscale Britannia community. Known
                for elegant architecture of its homes and beautiful landscapes, Britannia is located west of Elbow River
                and Elbow Drive. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The Riverdale Park is to the west side of Britannia, while to the north is Britannia
                Drive.Britannia became part of Calgary in 1910 and developed into a neighborhood in the 1950s.</p>

            <p class="par-lg">The upscale Britannia real estate features mostly single-family detached homes with condos
                and apartments forming a small part of the community. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Britannia real estate offers a great combination of tranquility and convenient location
                that is popular among families looking for long-term housing. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The average price of homes for sale in Britannia real estate is $2,995,000.00. Options
                range between $490,000 and $4,900,000.</p>

        </div>
